metadata.name: Old Men With White Beards Ad Nauseam #1/2
metadata.description:
This is a comment on the remarkable amount of OEs that have been minting as of late. This will have zero value. And will do nothing to make you feel better about life.

However, it is a lovely picture of a single Old Men With White Beard repeated in a pattern.

To be honest, it isn't really even balanced well at all. Oh well.

Reminder: This has no value whatsoever.
